data.description: **ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN AT 2.875%** available for qualifying buyers. Don't miss the opportunity to own one of the largest pool homes in the area and pay very low monthly mortgage payments! Conveniently located with easy access to shopping, dining and schools, in a tranquil and quiet neighborhood. Step inside to discover an open-concept living area bathed in natural light and a split floorplan. The huge and updated master bedroom and bath has direct access to the pool area. Granite countertop in the kitchen, separate laundry room and additional bar for entertainment. The super spacious and fenced in backyard is perfect for barbeque, hosting gatherings by the pool. Parking for boat. This oversized, 1,700sq+ home will provide plenty of space for your family. FHA, VA, Conventional buyers welcome.
